name: Cloud | With no previous trial and no current license should not show Upgrade button for admin users on non trial licensed server

inline.description:
Precondition: should not have a trial license
Test Steps
  1. 1: Login with admin
  2. 2: navigate to system console to verify 'Trial' badge on the license
  3. 3: Navigate back to channels
  4. 4: verify Upgrade button is not shown on the top banner
inline.expectedResult: Successfully Verify Upgrade button is not shown on the top banner
